## 7. Repository Implementation Workflow

When implementing OPRMT™ inside the repository, use this workflow:

```text
1. Define the purpose of the file or prompt asset.
2. Assign the correct repository folder.
3. Select the correct document or prompt type.
4. Apply the OPRMT™ structure where appropriate.
5. Add metadata or document header.
6. Add version number.
7. Add usage scope.
8. Add ownership notice.
9. Check for unsupported claims.
10. Submit through pull request review.
```

---

